  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ball
    Ball class is used to display circles on the grid for the game.
    Computer
    Computer class is used to make a simple AI opponent for single- player mode.
    GameOverController
    This class gives you three options when the game gets over 1.
    GamePage
    GamePage is the class used to signify the page the game will be played on.
    Grid
    Grid class is the main class for the game.
    MainController
    This class is the controller class for the main page.
    MainPage
    This is the Main Page class of the game from where the game starts It cotains the main functions and the main window on which our game will be working
    myRectangle
    myRectangle is a custom class inheriting from Rectangle and contains information of the coordinates in the grid they occupy.
    myStack<T>
    myStack class is a custom class inherited from the Stack class that limits the size of the stack to the defined maximum size.
    NewGameController
    This is the controller class for the New Game page It consists of 3 buttons 1.
    NewGameController2
    This is the controller class for the New Game page It consists of 3 buttons 1.
    P<T1,T2>
    This class is just like Pair class The only difference is in the toString function Which was needed to display in the choice-box used further
    Player
    The Player class is used to portray the players who are playing the game.
    quit2Controller
    This class is the controller class for exiting the game It asks the user to confirm the quit if they press the YES button This class is active when the game gets over and user decides to exit
    quitController
    This class is the controller class for exiting the game It asks the user to confirm the quit if they press the YES button This class is active when the game has not started yet and the user decides to exit
    SelectPlayerController
    This is the controller class for Selecting number of players and the grid size in which they want to play Buttons: 1.
    SerializableBall
    A Serializable version of the Ball class.
    SettingsController
    This class is the controller class for Settings page This page consists of 8 Color Pickers corresponding to the 8 players
